1
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:40,980
=Cinta Di Luar Kubur=
(Diadaptasi daripada novel oleh Li Qingran)

2
00:01:41,260 --> 00:01:43,990
=Episod 22=

3
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:50,630
Jika itu sahaja, anda boleh pergi.

4
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,580
Jangan hanya berdiri di sini.

5
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:53,780
Betapa menjengkelkan.

6
00:01:59,910 --> 00:02:00,750
Yang Mulia,

7
00:02:01,220 --> 00:02:02,910
Saya dengar Her Ladyship mengambil seorang manusia

8
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:04,140
ke Penjara Sembilan Persegi Maze.

9
00:02:04,670 --> 00:02:06,220
Dia melanggar Dekri Dinding Emas.

10
00:02:06,550 --> 00:02:07,830
Ya, Yang Mulia.

11
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:09,990
Jika anda tidak pergi ke sana secara peribadi,

12
00:02:10,230 --> 00:02:11,790
yang fana itu akan mati.

13
00:02:12,830 --> 00:02:14,700
Ladyship dengan sengaja melanggar undang-undang

14
00:02:14,860 --> 00:02:16,140
dan cuba membunuh seorang manusia.

15
00:02:16,550 --> 00:02:17,390
Ia...

16
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,700
Ia satu kesalahan besar.

17
00:02:19,230 --> 00:02:20,580
- Betul.
- Ya.

18
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:21,580
fana?

19
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:23,390
Hanya ada seorang manusia di sini.

20
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:25,510
Saya mendengar lilin jiwanya

21
00:02:25,510 --> 00:02:26,390
telah dipadamkan.

22
00:02:26,620 --> 00:02:27,620
Dia terselamat pula.

23
00:02:28,180 --> 00:02:29,670
Saya tertanya-tanya adakah Her Grace

24
00:02:29,830 --> 00:02:31,460
melakukan sesuatu di dalam Penjara.

25
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:34,350
Mungkinkah dia tercedera?

26
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,110
Yang Mulia,

27
00:02:37,350 --> 00:02:38,300
ia tidak sesuai

28
00:02:38,300 --> 00:02:39,140
untuk menutup kami di sini.

29
00:02:39,550 --> 00:02:41,180
Keluar dan buat keputusan.

30
00:02:42,110 --> 00:02:43,350
Yang Mulia,

31
00:02:43,350 --> 00:02:44,670
sila buat ketetapan.

32
00:03:01,140 --> 00:03:02,070
Macam bising.

33
00:03:03,670 --> 00:03:05,350
Salam, Yang Mulia.

34
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:08,270
Kenapa awak berhenti?

35
00:03:10,350 --> 00:03:12,250
Puterinya membawa seorang manusia ke Penjara

36
00:03:12,550 --> 00:03:13,470
dan melanggar undang-undang.

37
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:14,550
Yang Mulia,

38
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:15,810
menghukumnya mengikut undang-undang.

39
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:17,550
Apa pendapat anda, Jiang Ai?

40
00:03:18,230 --> 00:03:19,350
Mereka mahu kamu mati.

41
00:03:22,620 --> 00:03:24,670
Saya memang melanggar Dekri Golden-wall,

42
00:03:24,990 --> 00:03:26,390
tetapi manusia itu tidak mati.

43
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:27,700
Mengikut undang-undang,

44
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:28,950
Saya tidak layak untuk mati.

45
00:03:29,180 --> 00:03:30,670
Tetapi saya tetap bersalah.

46
00:03:31,140 --> 00:03:31,990
Saya akan dihukum.

47
00:03:33,790 --> 00:03:35,860
Yan Ke, kenapa awak senyap?

48
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:37,990
Apa pendapat anda?

49
00:03:43,020 --> 00:03:44,550
Sebagai Tangan Kiri, Jiang Ai

50
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:46,020
dengan sengaja melanggar perintah.

51
00:03:46,580 --> 00:03:48,180
Tiada bahaya serius telah dilakukan,

52
00:03:48,580 --> 00:03:50,550
maka perempuan itu hendaklah disebat tiga puluh kali.

53
00:03:51,390 --> 00:03:52,860
Bagi kesalahan lain,

54
00:03:53,140 --> 00:03:54,110
sila tentukan

55
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:55,860
mengikut undang-undang.

56
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:00,350
Mulai hari ini,

57
00:04:01,020 --> 00:04:02,860
Jiang Ai akan merenung kesilapannya.

58
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:04,580
Tugasnya akan sementara

59
00:04:04,950 --> 00:04:06,180
dikendalikan oleh Yan Ke.

60
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,140
Mulai sekarang,

61
00:04:08,740 --> 00:04:10,300
tiada siapa boleh menceroboh

62
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,270
dalam Penjara.

63
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:13,620
Sebatan

64
00:04:16,110 --> 00:04:18,380
akan dilaksanakan oleh Yan Ke.

65
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:20,670
serta merta.

66
00:04:23,150 --> 00:04:23,990
ya.

67
00:04:26,420 --> 00:04:28,060
Rahmatnya masih memihak kepada Yang Mulia.

68
00:04:29,350 --> 00:04:30,380
Dia tidak akan menunjukkan pilih kasih

69
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:33,030
semasa hukuman sebat.

70
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:41,860
Adakah anda mempunyai sebarang aduan?

71
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:44,030
Her Grace memerintahkan anda untuk melakukan ini.

72
00:04:44,590 --> 00:04:45,740
Saya percaya

73
00:04:45,740 --> 00:04:47,590
anda telah memahami apa yang dia maksudkan.

74
00:04:48,180 --> 00:04:49,260
Jadi saya tiada aduan.

75
00:04:54,910 --> 00:04:56,230
Semua orang ada di sini hari ini.

76
00:04:56,420 --> 00:04:58,060
Kemudian lakukan sekarang.

77
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:00,550
Jangan rosakkan mood Her Grace.

78
00:05:18,990 --> 00:05:20,860
Anda cuba menyingkirkan saya,

79
00:05:21,230 --> 00:05:23,230
tetapi tidak pernah mengharapkan RahmatNya
untuk melindungi saya secara terbuka.

80
00:05:24,230 --> 00:05:25,820
Sekarang bahawa plot anda telah gagal,

81
00:05:26,350 --> 00:05:27,190
tak rasa teruk ke?

82
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,710
Dua puluh lapan sebatan lagi.

83
00:05:40,150 --> 00:05:41,620
Masa anda untuk mendera saya

84
00:05:41,620 --> 00:05:42,460
hampir habis.

85
00:05:50,790 --> 00:05:52,420
Apa yang berlaku hari ini

86
00:05:54,030 --> 00:05:56,260
adalah jauh lebih buruk daripada yang saya fikirkan.

87
00:06:00,180 --> 00:06:01,030
Her Grace biasanya

88
00:06:01,030 --> 00:06:02,110
bergantung pada Tuan Puan.

89
00:06:02,590 --> 00:06:03,500
Tetapi dia tidak menunjukkan belas kasihan

90
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:04,910
dalam hukuman.

91
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:08,230
Kerana Yang Mulia tidak mempunyai hati.

92
00:06:08,230 --> 00:06:09,420
Seolah-olah anda mempunyai satu.

93
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,860
Hei.

94
00:06:10,860 --> 00:06:11,990
Jangan libatkan saya.

95
00:06:12,470 --> 00:06:13,310
Anda semua,

96
00:06:14,350 --> 00:06:15,670
dengarlah.

97
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:19,110
Sesiapa yang melanggar
Dekri Tembok Emas

98
00:06:19,710 --> 00:06:21,110
akan berakhir begini.

99
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:27,950
Simu.

100
00:06:31,030 --> 00:06:32,150
Suara fana itu.

101
00:06:36,590 --> 00:06:37,430
Selepas sebatan,

102
00:06:38,180 --> 00:06:39,020
anda semua boleh pergi.

103
00:06:43,470 --> 00:06:45,670
Nyonyanya benar-benar menderita.

104
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:09,260
Selepas bertahun-tahun ini,

105
00:08:11,230 --> 00:08:13,820
Saya dihukum lagi kerana dia.

106
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:17,860
Bai Sanxing, saya benci awak!

107
00:08:18,710 --> 00:08:19,550
Saya...

108
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:21,860
(Saya akan bayar balik)

109
00:08:22,860 --> 00:08:24,470
(seratus kali ganda.)

110
00:08:26,710 --> 00:08:27,990
(Saya selamatkan awak)

111
00:08:27,990 --> 00:08:28,860
(dari roh jahat.)

112
00:08:29,990 --> 00:08:31,670
(Awak sepatutnya sentiasa menjadi milik saya.)

113
00:08:41,580 --> 00:08:42,540
Tuan Puan.

114
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:04,430
boleh saya jumpa awak?

115
00:09:16,830 --> 00:09:17,670
Masuklah.

116
00:09:25,190 --> 00:09:26,190
Salam, Tuan Puan.

117
00:09:31,430 --> 00:09:33,190
Ini ialah Glacial Elixir, satu penghormatan

118
00:09:33,190 --> 00:09:34,540
dari Tanah Frigid tahun lepas.

119
00:09:34,990 --> 00:09:36,350
Ia menyembuhkan luka dengan cepat.

120
00:09:43,620 --> 00:09:45,070
Tuanku terlalu kejam.

121
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:46,950
Cambuk Tulang Belakangnya

122
00:09:47,260 --> 00:09:48,860
diperbuat daripada Thunderous Crystal Keel.

123
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:51,590
Apabila dia menyebat kamu,
dia juga menggunakan tenaga rohani.

124
00:09:52,310 --> 00:09:53,500
Semangat biasa

125
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:54,620
akan dimusnahkan

126
00:09:54,620 --> 00:09:55,830
selepas hanya satu sebatan.

127
00:09:58,660 --> 00:10:00,740
Dia berharap saya akan dimusnahkan.

128
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:03,430
Sayang sekali dia tidak dapat membunuh saya.

129
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,660
Sekarang, dia bertanggungjawab ke atas Kuil Xuling,

130
00:10:08,230 --> 00:10:09,860
tapi semua orang setia dengan saya.

131
00:10:10,430 --> 00:10:11,860
Dia tidak akan mendapat apa-apa daripadanya.

132
00:10:14,430 --> 00:10:16,380
Jangan risau sangat.

133
00:10:18,380 --> 00:10:19,950
Sekarang dia ada masalah baru

134
00:10:19,950 --> 00:10:20,900
untuk berurusan dengan.

135
00:10:21,430 --> 00:10:22,590
Dia tiada masa untuk saya.

136
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:27,740
Masalah baru?

137
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:31,230
Apa yang membawa anda ke sini?

138
00:10:32,430 --> 00:10:34,260
Elixir tonik fana telah tiba.

139
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:36,190
Jika anda tidak boleh pergi,

140
00:10:36,190 --> 00:10:37,310
Saya akan ambilkan untuk awak.

141
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:38,620
tak perlu.

142
00:10:40,430 --> 00:10:41,660
Semakin ramai yang berfikir

143
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:43,230
Saya telah jatuh,

144
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:45,430
semakin saya perlu bertindak seperti biasa.

145
00:11:00,310 --> 00:11:01,230
Salam, Yang Mulia.

146
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:02,780
Kenapa awak datang ke sini

147
00:11:02,780 --> 00:11:03,620
bukannya berehat?

148
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:05,070
Cuma cedera ringan.

149
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:07,830
Elixir toniknya telah tiba.

150
00:11:08,020 --> 00:11:09,020
Saya telah membawanya kepadanya.

151
00:11:13,990 --> 00:11:14,830
Simu,

152
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:18,590
di Penjara Sembilan Persegi Maze,

153
00:11:18,590 --> 00:11:20,230
Bai Sanxing tiba-tiba menyerang kami.

154
00:11:20,710 --> 00:11:22,230
Untuk menyelamatkan saya,

155
00:11:22,380 --> 00:11:24,190
dia kehilangan lilin jiwanya dan tersesat.

156
00:11:25,020 --> 00:11:26,310
Di sana, dia bertaruh dengan saya.

157
00:11:26,660 --> 00:11:28,190
Jika dia berjaya kembali hidup,

158
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:30,140
Saya akan memberitahu dia tentang masa lalu anda.

159
00:11:30,740 --> 00:11:32,110
Apabila dia bangun,

160
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:34,310
patutkah saya menghormati pertaruhan saya?

161
00:11:36,590 --> 00:11:37,780
Awak boleh beritahu dia.

162
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:39,070
ya.

163
00:11:43,430 --> 00:11:44,710
Adakah anda benci Bai Sanxing?

164
00:11:53,310 --> 00:11:54,350
Sudah tentu.

165
00:11:56,070 --> 00:11:57,500
Sebab tu saya tipu dia

166
00:11:57,500 --> 00:11:59,020
ke dalam Penjara Sembilan Persegi Maze

167
00:11:59,020 --> 00:12:01,230
dan berusaha keras untuk menyingkirkannya.

168
00:12:03,780 --> 00:12:05,470
Jika tubuh seseorang terkurung,

169
00:12:06,950 --> 00:12:07,990
dia boleh membebaskan diri.

170
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:11,430
Tetapi jika hatinya ditawan,

171
00:12:13,230 --> 00:12:14,540
dia hanya akan rela

172
00:12:14,540 --> 00:12:15,620
mengurung dirinya.

173
00:12:16,900 --> 00:12:17,780
Anda patut tahu

174
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:19,110
apa sebenarnya yang ada dalam hati awak.

175
00:12:24,900 --> 00:12:26,430
Kemudian bagaimana dengan anda?

176
00:12:27,540 --> 00:12:28,710
Hari ini, anda telah

177
00:12:28,710 --> 00:12:30,230
tinggal di tepi katilnya

178
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:32,140
dan menjaganya dengan teliti.

179
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:34,380
Anda juga mempunyai perhimpunan pagi di sini.

180
00:12:34,540 --> 00:12:36,070
Tapi awak enggan terima dia.

181
00:12:37,070 --> 00:12:38,950
Bolehkah anda menghadapi apa yang ada dalam hati anda sendiri?

182
00:12:44,260 --> 00:12:45,100
Simu,

183
00:12:45,710 --> 00:12:47,070
apa yang awak takutkan?

184
00:13:28,470 --> 00:13:29,310
Bagaimana pula

185
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:30,740
awak simpan saya di sisi awak?

186
00:13:31,430 --> 00:13:32,500
Bila-bila masa anda mahu merasa,

187
00:13:33,430 --> 00:13:34,380
anda boleh mempunyai deria saya.

188
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:35,980
Simu!

189
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:38,110
Untuk manusia, kekal dalam Kekosongan

190
00:13:38,470 --> 00:13:39,380
adalah lebih menakutkan

191
00:13:40,070 --> 00:13:41,140
daripada kematian.

192
00:13:42,190 --> 00:13:43,070
Jadi apa?

193
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:47,990
(Pada masa itu, saya lemah semangat.)

194
00:13:49,500 --> 00:13:50,470
(Saya merindui ringkas itu)

195
00:13:50,470 --> 00:13:51,660
(namun persahabatan yang manis.)

196
00:13:54,540 --> 00:13:55,860
Saya pasti akan menghargai

197
00:13:55,860 --> 00:13:56,990
tengkorak pintar anda.

198
00:13:57,500 --> 00:13:58,340
Foxy,

199
00:13:58,660 --> 00:13:59,990
biar saya rasa.

200
00:14:02,990 --> 00:14:04,020
(Saya mendambakan kehangatan)

201
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:05,590
(dan kelembutan dunia.)

202
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:07,620
(Jadi saya bawa awak kembali ke Void.)

203
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:12,430
(Kekosongan dengan malam yang tidak berkesudahan.)

204
00:14:15,140 --> 00:14:16,830
(Tetapi anda bukan milik di sini, lagipun.)

205
00:14:17,950 --> 00:14:19,260
(Awak tidak tergolong dalam dunia saya.)

206
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:23,540
(Walaupun saya boleh memiliki awak seketika,)

207
00:14:23,950 --> 00:14:25,860
(Saya pasti akan kehilangan awak suatu hari nanti.)

208
00:14:27,230 --> 00:14:28,230
(Dalam kes itu,)

209
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:31,190
(apa gunanya bermula?)

210
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:54,340
Simu.

211
00:15:52,660 --> 00:15:53,500
Hanya apabila saya sakit

212
00:15:53,500 --> 00:15:54,990
bolehkah saya dilayan dengan baik.

213
00:16:08,140 --> 00:16:09,230
Saya betul-betul terjaga.

214
00:16:18,740 --> 00:16:19,590
Hebat.

215
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:22,220
Ini hebat.

216
00:16:23,230 --> 00:16:24,950
Saya masih boleh melihat wajah anda yang tersenyum.

217
00:16:28,070 --> 00:16:28,910
Hebat.

218
00:16:32,140 --> 00:16:33,900
Anda masih mahu melihat wajah ini.

219
00:16:45,310 --> 00:16:46,150
Simu,

220
00:16:48,230 --> 00:16:49,070
saya minta maaf.

221
00:16:51,640 --> 00:16:52,540
Anda telah

222
00:16:52,540 --> 00:16:53,900
melalui banyak kenangan yang mengerikan.

223
00:16:56,170 --> 00:16:57,020
Saya tahu

224
00:16:57,020 --> 00:16:57,990
awak benci perpisahan.

225
00:16:59,950 --> 00:17:01,140
Tetapi saya masih membenarkan anda

226
00:17:01,140 --> 00:17:02,350
lihat saya menjadi tua.

227
00:17:08,470 --> 00:17:09,500
Maaf, Simu.

228
00:17:11,670 --> 00:17:13,230
Saya tidak ada untuk awak sepanjang masa.

229
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:18,150
Itu adalah ilusi,

230
00:17:21,410 --> 00:17:23,300
tetapi saya percaya semua kegembiraan dan kegembiraan

231
00:17:24,540 --> 00:17:25,500
adalah nyata.

232
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:29,020
Alangkah baiknya, Simu.

233
00:17:30,770 --> 00:17:31,630
Saya sangat gembira

234
00:17:31,630 --> 00:17:32,990
bahawa anda juga mempunyai perasaan untuk saya.

235
00:17:35,100 --> 00:17:36,710
Saya suka bersama awak juga.

236
00:17:52,820 --> 00:17:54,020
Jika anda masih menyukainya,

237
00:17:56,540 --> 00:17:58,190
kita boleh beli rumah.

238
00:17:59,630 --> 00:18:00,950
Dengan gunung dan air di sekelilingnya.

239
00:18:02,300 --> 00:18:03,740
Kami akan menanam pokok buah-buahan dan bunga

240
00:18:04,950 --> 00:18:07,020
belakang gunung.

241
00:18:12,260 --> 00:18:13,670
Anda sangat menyukai ketumbar.

242
00:18:14,390 --> 00:18:15,500
Kami hanya akan menanam ketumbar

243
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:16,500
sepanjang aliran.

244
00:18:24,170 --> 00:18:25,030
Saya tidak faham

245
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:26,100
kenapa anda suka rasa ini.

246
00:18:26,230 --> 00:18:27,950
Buat kuih bulan isi ketumbar lagi?

247
00:18:28,910 --> 00:18:30,300
Anda suka kuih bulan berisi ketumbar.

248
00:18:31,390 --> 00:18:32,910
Kemudian kami akan meletakkan lebih banyak kacang tanah yang telah dihancurkan

249
00:18:35,580 --> 00:18:36,500
dan gula batu.

250
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:48,940
