314
00:25:55,150 --> 00:25:57,060
Saya menyuapkan dia ramuan penghapus ingatan.

315
00:25:59,580 --> 00:26:01,260
Dia mungkin tidak akan ingat apa-apa.

316
00:26:05,060 --> 00:26:05,910
